    "John Phillips is an angel investor who made an early bet on Shopify, a Canadian e-commerce software company.",
    "He and his wife Catherine Phillips together own an estimated 2% of Shopify.",
    "John served on Shopify's board of directors from 2010 to 2023.",
    "The couple has invested in a slew of other early-stage companies that are lesser known, like Virtual Marine Technology and Sequence Bio.",
    "John previously spent 25 years as a corporate lawyer, including as general counsel at telecom firm Clearnet Communications.",
    "The Phillips' Northpine Foundation has donated hundreds of millions to organizations focused on climate, refugees and formerly incarcerated individuals."
